LINUX

* Add path to $PATH variable:
	- in files ~/.bashrc or ~/.bash_profile add:
			export PATH="~/.composer/vendor/bin:$PATH"
			// or...
			export PATH="$HOME/.composer/vendor/bin:$PATH"
			// or to the end of $PATH
			export PATH="$PATH:$HOME/.composer/vendor/bin"
			
* Check hard disk
		- df
		- df -H
